    <DisplayName>Velo – DORA Metrics &amp; AI Pipeline Intelligence for Azure DevOps</DisplayName>
    <GalleryFlags>Public</GalleryFlags>
    <Description xml:space="preserve">Track all 5 DORA metrics automatically from Azure DevOps pipelines and PRs, with an AI agent for delivery insights.</Description>
